      "comment": "REIGN 'EM IN (6) all three career runs have been sound and should be able to get control from the low gate today. Nailed late in a fast-run contest when third over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Key jockey change and comes here in peak condition. MONOCRU (4) slow into stride second-up and never got into the contest with a battling seventh over 1100m at this track. Fitter now and expect to see her race a touch closer. COSMIC ORDER (1) covered a stack of ground on debut with a plugging sixth over 900m at Newcastle on the Heavy (9) surface. Should come on from that run from the inside barrier. SHANGRI LA ROSE (8) is on debut and has the right profile to figure in the finish.",
